Salt Bae, whose real name is Nusret Gokce is a Turkish chef who s taken social-media by storm. He caught everyone s attention after a video of him seasoning stake went viral. A lot of celebs have been showing him a lot of love, even pop sensation, Rihanna recently rocked a T-shirt inspired by him. There is just something about the way this guy sprinkles salt on his food it s so unique. Funny Memes inspired by Nusret have been all over the internet since he broke out. Check out our top 5 memes below and let us know what you think. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Brought to you by People Magazine For more news your way, follow The Citizen on Facebook and Twitter.